      <description>&lt;p&gt;Check out the project on &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Duks31/capp&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;github&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;demos&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Demo&amp;rsquo;s&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#demos&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div style= &#34;overflow-x : auto;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Demo 1&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Demo 2&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Demo 3&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Demo 4&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/capp_demo_1.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Demo_1&#34;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/capp_demo_2.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Demo_2&#34;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/capp_demo_3.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Demo_3&#34;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/capp_demo_4.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Demo_4&#34;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;description&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Description&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#description&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The Chat App is a user-friendly messaging application that allows you to connect and communicate with friends and family. It is a simple and easy-to-use app that allows you to send and receive messages. The Chat App is a great way to stay connected with the people you care about, no matter where they are in the world.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
